data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 bedroom ranch, boasting a fully fenced yard on a corner lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by original woodwork, complemented by newer windows and vinyl plank flooring that extends throughout most of the home. The dining room showcases stunning built-in shelving and a generous picture window, while the kitchen offers a newer gas stove and retro refrigerator. The bathroom has been tastefully updated with a tiled tub surround, vanity, and modern lighting. Outside, the backyard is fully fenced and features a patio accessible from the back door. This home has undergone numerous updates, including a new furnace, A/C, hot water tank, and some plumbing. Don't miss the opportunity to see this delightful property!
